narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This was a challenging course in terms of reading load, but it was simultaneously fascinating and incredibly enriching. It is difficult to describe the level and breadth of knowledge gained from this course; I will only say that it was substantial and very valuable to me. I feel very lucky to have been able to be part of this course.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This course was fantastic though challenging. I would recommend it to very dedicated and intellectually engaged students.
